sequenceDiagram
    participant Code as Code
    participant TraitObj as Box<dyn Trait>
    participant Concrete as Concrete Type
    participant Any as Any trait

    Code->>TraitObj: Create trait object
    TraitObj-->>Code: Box<dyn Trait>
    
    Code->>TraitObj: downcast_ref<SpecificType>()
    TraitObj->>Any: Check type_id
    Any-->>TraitObj: Match?

    alt Type matches
        TraitObj-->>Code: Some(&SpecificType)
        Code->>Concrete: Use concrete methods
    else Type doesn't match
        TraitObj-->>Code: None
        Code->>Code: Try other type
    end

    Note over Code,Any: Requires Any trait - Runtime type checking
